product.name: Custom Photo Crystal Car Hanging Ornaments Personalized Car Rearview Mirror Accessories for Women Men
product.bullet_points:
• 【Custom Car Ornament Crystal Pendant】：You can choose your favorite photos to customize your exclusive car crystal pendant, such as photos of your family, friends and pets. Click the customize button, choose your favorite crystal pendant style and upload your photo to make the customization. easily.
• 【Unique Design】：This crystal pendant car hanging ornament has a symbolic meaning of happiness and good luck. Each crystal is finely cut and the crystal is crystal clear and shines under the light.
• 【Ideal Size】：The crystal pendant car ornament measures approximately 13 inches in length and weighs approximately 0.35 pounds. The lanyard is just the right length so it doesn't block the view. The size of different styles may be different, please refer to the size chart we provide for the specific size.
• 【Suitable Scenes】：You can hang on crystal pendant car mirror hanging accessories the rearview mirror of the car, which will make people feel better while beautifying the environment inside the car. You can also decorate the crystal pendants on windowsills, Christmas trees and wedding party favors to make life more artistic.
• 【Perfect Gift】：The special customized crystal pendant car hanging accessories has a memorial meaning to express love, affection and friendship. This crystal pendant would be a great choice as a gift for family and friends, or a perfect gift for Valentine's Day, Christmas, birthdays, anniversaries, Mother's Day, Father's Day or a special anniversary.
